	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-27092">

                <div class="fullcomment">

		<div class="com-top"></div>	

		<div class="com-mid">

			
			<h5><cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.sidewaysface.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Rebecca</a></cite> said:</h5>
      
			<p>That looks amazing! And I love how you lay every step out so clearly so even I have a chance at making it <img src='http://backtothecuttingboard.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif' alt=':P' class='wp-smiley' /><br />
<span class="cluv">Rebecca´s last [type] ..<a class="54647c15cd 27092" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.sidewaysface.com/2011/09/the-classy-fabulous-unmistakable-propeller-cap/">The Classy, Fabulous, Unmistakable Propeller Cap</a></span></p>

			<p class="commentmetadata"><a href="http://backtothecuttingboard.com/dessert/spiced-apple-and-pear-shortcakes-apple-scones/#comment-27092">September 26, 2011 at 11:16 am</a>  | <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/dessert/spiced-apple-and-pear-shortcakes-apple-scones/?replytocom=27092#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("-27092", "27092", "respond", "2772")'>Reply</a></p>

		</div>

		<div class="com-bot"></div>	

