                <h4>Featured Recipe</h4>
		<div class="featured">
                	                        	<a href="http://backtothecuttingboard.com/breakfast/pumpkin-cinnamon-streusal-buns/"><img width="250" height="166" src="http://backtothecuttingboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/pumpkin-buns1-250x166.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Pumpkin-Cinnamon Streusal Buns" title="pumpkin-buns1" /></a>
                        	Pumpkin-Cinnamon Streusel Buns                				</div>

